{
  "stem": "8775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and he was, he was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a devout Nazi as, as you can get.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, there was the SS person there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he walked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he watched everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he watched everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he perhaps watched even the, the duchess and, and the count.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One of the, the ladies, the duchess' daughter, was married to a count.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they lived in another place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the only connection we had with them that they saw us, and we saw them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And once, or a few times, me and a friend of mine were invited to bring woods into their kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we got a little extra treat, you know, a little milk or something, a little bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we lived in a deep forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We lived in a little-- well, actually the place where it was was at the border of Austria and Czechoslovakia, which used to be Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was a river there named Thaya River.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And where they put us was a little border post, border, a guard post, by the river on the Austrian side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were told never try to, to escape by swimming over the river.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because we would perish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We would be shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because they were watching the river.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, of course, both sides belonged to Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But still, they were watching the river.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So-- but where we lived, there was nobody around us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Only 21 of us lived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there was one man who was the-- our commandant, who was the head of, head of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was an orthodox Jew from Szolnok, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And his name was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, his name was Samuel, S-A-M-U-E-L.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His first name was Miksa, M-I-K-S-A.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was there with his wife and his daughter.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
